00:06:58.821 --> 00:07:00.421
Sometimes, in spiritual circles,

162
00:07:00.421 --> 00:07:02.651
people can get pretty sacrosanct, you know?

163
00:07:02.651 --> 00:07:05.850
And just replace the old religious observances

164
00:07:05.850 --> 00:07:07.568
with the new spiritual disciplines,

165
00:07:07.568 --> 00:07:10.287
and the old religious hierarchy

166
00:07:10.287 --> 00:07:13.111
with the new gurus or whatever.

167
00:07:13.111 --> 00:07:16.166
And it's just the same, more of the same thing.

168
00:07:16.166 --> 00:07:19.249
Mistaking the path for the power.

169
00:07:19.249 --> 00:07:21.617
And I have a, my coach,

170
00:07:21.617 --> 00:07:24.550
I have a coach and an ex-boyfriend who says,

171
00:07:24.550 --> 00:07:25.915
"Nothing works.

172
00:07:25.915 --> 00:07:29.862
"Nothing works. It's all intention."

173
00:07:29.862 --> 00:07:31.216
It's all what you do, you know?

174
00:07:31.216 --> 00:07:33.189
So you can have your crystals or your this or your that,

175
00:07:33.189 --> 00:07:35.269
and you're going to those conscious life expos,

176
00:07:35.269 --> 00:07:37.872
and there's thousands of things, you know?

177
00:07:37.872 --> 00:07:40.080
Gurus, teachers, whatever.

178
00:07:40.080 --> 00:07:42.351
I think you have to actually

179
00:07:42.351 --> 00:07:45.071
see the hypocrisy in a few gurus,

180
00:07:45.071 --> 00:07:49.319
get completely-- feel betrayed by them, forgive them,

181
00:07:49.319 --> 00:07:52.522
and then maybe get on your spiritual path.

182
00:07:52.522 --> 00:07:53.664
<v ->(laughing) Right.</v>

