184
00:07:55.594 --> 00:07:56.746
<v ->Right.</v>

185
00:07:56.746 --> 00:07:58.378
<v ->You know? So I've done a lot of that.</v>

186
00:07:58.378 --> 00:07:59.882
<v ->Yeah, I think most people,</v>

187
00:07:59.882 --> 00:08:01.439
probably most people watching this,

188
00:08:01.439 --> 00:08:03.135
have done exactly the same thing as well.

189
00:08:03.135 --> 00:08:04.063
<v ->Yeah.</v>

190
00:08:04.063 --> 00:08:05.855
<v ->You know, we tend to want to hang on to something</v>

191
00:08:05.855 --> 00:08:08.127
while we're looking at this in-between place in life.

