00:08:08.127 --> 00:08:09.823
And so you were...

193
00:08:09.823 --> 00:08:12.446
One of the things I was intrigued with

194
00:08:12.446 --> 00:08:13.886
was your whole journey with Ramtha.

195
00:08:13.886 --> 00:08:15.028
What was that like for you?

196
00:08:15.028 --> 00:08:16.137
What were you there for?

