00:08:25.390 --> 00:08:28.619
that there is no ultimate duality in the universe.

201
00:08:28.619 --> 00:08:30.027
And I loved that.

202
00:08:30.027 --> 00:08:31.701
<v ->And that goes back to when you were a kid,</v>

203
00:08:31.701 --> 00:08:33.163
when you had your little trip.

204
00:08:33.163 --> 00:08:34.123
<v ->Yeah.</v>

205
00:08:34.123 --> 00:08:35.445
<v ->When you knew you were one with everything.</v>

206
00:08:35.445 --> 00:08:36.554
<v ->Yeah.</v>

207
00:08:36.554 --> 00:08:37.898
<v ->So was she the next time you hooked in with that,</v>

208
00:08:37.898 --> 00:08:38.880
many years later?

209
00:08:38.880 --> 00:08:40.085
<v ->Yeah.</v>

210
00:08:40.085 --> 00:08:41.685
I remember actually lying in a field with my brother,

211
00:08:41.685 --> 00:08:43.381
and saying, there has to be...

212
00:08:43.381 --> 00:08:44.757
No one's telling us the truth.

213
00:08:44.757 --> 00:08:45.983
They're pretending that they know the truth,

214
00:08:45.983 --> 00:08:48.138
and they're putting information down our throats,

215
00:08:48.138 --> 00:08:50.618
and saying this is the truth, believe this.

216
00:08:50.618 --> 00:08:54.313
But none of it explains the vast magnificence of this.

217
00:08:54.313 --> 00:08:57.780
There has to be like a genie,

218
00:08:57.780 --> 00:09:00.069
like a someone.

219
00:09:00.069 --> 00:09:01.285
Someone who knows.

220
00:09:01.285 --> 00:09:02.629
There has to be someone who knows.

221
00:09:02.629 --> 00:09:04.922
You know, and just wishing for that.

222
00:09:04.922 --> 00:09:06.576
And then when Ramtha came along,

223
00:09:06.576 --> 00:09:09.650
there was a couple of supernormal things that happened

224
00:09:09.650 --> 00:09:12.311
that had my ears perk up.

225
00:09:12.311 --> 00:09:16.844
You know, I had never had supernormal experiences before.

226
00:09:16.844 --> 00:09:20.374
And then, I was living in New York City.

227
00:09:20.374 --> 00:09:22.091
My brother hands me an audio tape, says

228
00:09:22.091 --> 00:09:24.150
"This is a multi-dimensional entity.

229
00:09:24.150 --> 00:09:26.635
"If you call him into your life..."

230
00:09:26.635 --> 00:09:28.662
Him being the 35,000 year old warrior

231
00:09:28.662 --> 00:09:30.933
who is allegedly channeled by J. Z. Knight,

232
00:09:30.933 --> 00:09:33.184
I don't know what's going on, who knows?

233
00:09:33.184 --> 00:09:37.045
But there's something remarkable there.

234
00:09:37.045 --> 00:09:39.381
And so he said,

235
00:09:39.381 --> 00:09:41.642
"If you call him into your life, he'll appear."

236
00:09:41.642 --> 00:09:43.615
And I'm like, yeah, right, whatever.

237
00:09:43.615 --> 00:09:47.679
And so, I'm a waitress on 72nd and...

238
00:09:47.679 --> 00:09:48.810
What was it?

239
00:09:48.810 --> 00:09:51.644
Hamburger, Diane's Hamburgers in New York.

240
00:09:51.644 --> 00:09:54.324
And I go, all right, okay Ramtha,

241
00:09:54.324 --> 00:09:56.852
if you're really there, come into my life, right?

242
00:09:56.852 --> 00:09:59.401
And that day, two guys walk in the restaurant.

243
00:09:59.401 --> 00:10:01.118
I was singing. I go,

244
00:10:01.118 --> 00:10:04.030
♫ I need love, love, to help me ease my mind ♫

245
00:10:04.030 --> 00:10:05.769
And they go, and I turn around and go, oh!

246
00:10:05.769 --> 00:10:07.976
Did you come in to see me, or did you come to eat?

247
00:10:07.976 --> 00:10:09.672
And they go, oh, we came in to see you.

248
00:10:09.672 --> 00:10:11.987
And it was just like that kind of fun communication.

249
00:10:11.987 --> 00:10:14.099
And I said, well, we're not open yet,

250
00:10:14.099 --> 00:10:16.051
but just sit down, and I'll get to you.

251
00:10:16.051 --> 00:10:19.976
And so I walked up, and I said, isn't that funny,

252
00:10:19.976 --> 00:10:22.066
how when you're in a good mood,

253
00:10:22.066 --> 00:10:24.178
everyone around you seems to be in a good mood.

254
00:10:24.178 --> 00:10:25.501
And this guy goes,

